<section id="fs-id1172102063857" class="critical-thinking">
<title>Gagnrýnin hugsun</title>
<exercise id="fs-id1172099476885">
<problem id="fs-id1172099413126">
<para id="fs-id1172101775767">Frumveran sem sýnd er hefur hvað af eftirfarandi?</para>
<list id="fs-id1172101761944" list-type="enumerated" number-style="upper-alpha">
<item>pseudopodia</item>
<item>flagella</item>
<item>a shell</item>
